snippet.title: Skye - Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
A hyper-realistic Viking survival adventure, Skye is set in a vast 256sq km recreation of the Isle of Skye off the coast of Scotland.

Heading to Steam Early Access in 2022.

Wishlist the game on Steam!
https://bit.ly/SkyeSteam

Find all our socials on our LinkTree!
https://linktr.ee/AuroraGameStudios

www.auroragamestudios.co.uk
